channel.title: Xen (Open Beta) - Trailer | Robert Culp
channel.description:
It was getting near Robert Culp's birthday again and I had recently wrapped the first draft of a Half Life movie I was making, so I figured I'd do something special since I appreciate the guy so much. He really did change voice acting for me personally: I think he's the best there ever was.
Since Xen just came out in open-beta, I thought I'd throw this together since it was close enough. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WN3Ne-B719w&feature=youtu.be
